{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Bloxpath is a minimalist puzzle indie game based on rolling blocks, inspired by the classic Flash game &quot;Bloxorz.&quot; In this game, you can experience the purest joy of puzzle-solving, exploring various possibilities of the rolling mechanism among numerous puzzles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game features about 10 unique puzzle mechanics, each offering a new perspective on puzzle-solving.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249900/extras/Movie_011-3-4.gif?t=1737014291\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are approximately 150 puzzles in total, and the game places no restrictions on your solving order, allowing you to play at your own pace.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The overall difficulty of the game is moderate, so even non-core puzzle players can enjoy the fun of thinking critically.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">For core puzzle players, the game offers a large number of high-difficulty reward levels for you to conquer one by one.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249900/extras/Movie_011-4-3.gif?t=1737014291\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">While you rack your brains, you are accompanied by relaxing music and satisfying procedural animations that even appease perfectionists.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249900/extras/Movie_011-5-3.gif?t=1737014291\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249900/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737014291","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249900/page.bg.jpg?t=1737014291","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steam